## нҙҒ Pipeline CI/CD

El proyecto implementa dos pipelines complementarios:

### GitHub Actions (`.github/workflows/ci-cd.yml`)
Pipeline principal que se ejecuta automГЎticamente en cada push o pull request:

```
Trigger: push / pull_request
    в”Ӯ
    в”ңв”Җв”Җ Stage 1: Validate
    в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ terraform fmt -check
    в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ terraform validate
    в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ tflint (linting de HCL)
    в”Ӯ
    в”ңв”Җв”Җ Stage 2: Security & Quality
    в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ SonarQube analysis (sonar-project.properties)
    в”Ӯ
    в”ңв”Җв”Җ Stage 3: Build
    в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ Docker build + push a ECR
    в”Ӯ
    в””в”Җв”Җ Stage 4: Deploy
        в””в”Җв”Җ ArgoCD sync (actualiza manifiestos)
```

### Jenkins (`Jenkinsfile`)
Pipeline declarativo de Jenkins como alternativa o complemento a GitHub Actions para entornos on-premise o integraciones corporativas.

